channel.title: Opening an Interface (Add friend)
channel.description:
Hey guys,
I'm currently trying to open the add friend interface in which the player types the name of their desired friend. However, every interface ID I find for it disconnects the player. I understand that this interface is probably not as simple as just using a command to open the interface. However I'm looking for any advice on how I can open this interface.
All help is appreciated.
Thank you.
